      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Martin Blume</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:133px;\"><a href=\"/File:Martinblume.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/c/c6/Martinblume.jpg\" width=\"131\" height=\"182\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Martinblume.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Martin Blume <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Martin Blume</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist and author of the chess <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <a href=\"/Arena\" title=\"Arena\">Arena</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, \nwritten in <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>. Martin also wrote a chess engine running under <a href=\"/MS-DOS\" title=\"MS-DOS\">DOS</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, \nwhich was never published <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Blume&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=219912\">Re: Arena GUI 0.78 Beta 4 by Martin Blume is available!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Blume</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2002</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=399984\">Re: Question for Martin Blume</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Blume</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=400061\">An open letter to Martin Blume</a> by <a href=\"/Peter_Skinner\" title=\"Peter Skinner\">Peter Skinner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 10, 2004</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Blume&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20020925204655fw_/http://www.playwitharena.com/directory/interviews/interviews.htm\">Arena, Interviews mit Prof. Dr. Robert Hyatt, Tim Mann und Martin Blume</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a> for <a href=\"/ChessBits\" title=\"ChessBits\">ChessBits</a>, No. 18, May 2002 (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)&#160;» <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a>, <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Robert Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/Tim_Mann\" title=\"Tim Mann\">Tim Mann</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20110515014838/http://www.playwitharena.com/?Newsticker:Archive_10\">Arena Chess GUI - Archive 10 | 154 Martin Blume Interview</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Michael_Diosi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Michael Diosi (page does not exist)\">Michael Diosi</a>, December 21, 2007 (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, German)</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Blume&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20020925204655fw_/http://www.playwitharena.com/directory/interviews/interviews.htm\">Arena, Interviews mit Prof. Dr. Robert Hyatt, Tim Mann und Martin Blume</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a> for <a href=\"/ChessBits\" title=\"ChessBits\">ChessBits</a>, No. 18, May 2002 (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=205522\">New and free WinBoard and UCI GUI \"Arena\" by Martin Blume (Germany) ...</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=219912\">Re: Arena GUI 0.78 Beta 4 by Martin Blume is available!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Blume</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 27, 2002</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20110515014838/http://www.playwitharena.com/?Newsticker:Archive_10\">Arena Chess GUI - Archive 10 | 154 Martin Blume Interview</a> by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Michael_Diosi&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Michael Diosi (page does not exist)\">Michael Diosi</a>, December 21, 2007 (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>, German)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=245615\">3 interviews about engine protocols with T. Mann, R. Hyatt and M. Blume</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 15, 2002</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228221013\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.021 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.022 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 85/1000000\nPreprocessor generated 